Tradecraft Leves

From Final Fantasy XIV Online Wiki
Jump to navigation Jump to search
See also: Guildleve

Constancy leves are ordinary single-turn-in quests with the levemete and turn-in target in the same zone. Ingenuity leves are also single-turn-in, but either send you out from the Major City to a zone or in from a zone to the Major City. Finally, Charity are so called triple-turn-in leves, where you can optionally submit items two additional times for extra experience and Gil.
